Partitioning:   It means to segregate the data into various directories according to partitioning column.
                It improves the speed of Select queries, as only the required data is scanned and retrieved.


example:    Partioning by department column in department table.
            
            1. /home/user/dept_table/deptname=Accounts
            2. /home/user/dept_table/deptname=HR
            3. /home/user/dept_table/deptname=Sales
